    <p>• A 9 Volt Battery</p>
    <p>• Conductive Dough (to make conductive dough heat the 0.5 cup water, 0.5 cup flour, 2 tablespoons of salt, 1 squeezed lemon and 0.5 teaspoon of vegetable oil in a pot over medium heat until it reaches desired consistency)</p>

